SchemaItem.Name: Project_FillMissingStageHistory
SchemaItem.M01:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <xsl:stylesheet xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" version="1.0" xmlns:AS="http://schema.advantages.cz/AsapFunctions" xmlns:date="http://exslt.org/dates-and-times" exclude-result-prefixes="AS date">
<xsl:param name="projectId"/> <xsl:param name="currentStageId"/> <xsl:param name="previousStageId"/> <xsl:param name="projectStageHistory"/> <xsl:param name="keyAccountId" />
<xsl:template match="ROOT"> <ROOT> <xsl:apply-templates select="ProjectCategoryStage"/> </ROOT> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="ProjectCategoryStage"> <xsl:variable name="stageId" select="@refProjectStageId"/> <xsl:variable name="historyEntry" select="$projectStageHistory/ROOT/ProjectStageHistory[@refProjectStageId = $stageId]"/> <xsl:variable name="prevHistoryEntry" select="$projectStageHistory/ROOT/ProjectStageHistory[@refProjectStageId = $previousStageId]"/>
<xsl:choose> <!-- stage does not exist in the history, we create one --> <xsl:when test="not(string($historyEntry/@Id))"> <ProjectStageHistory Id="{AS:GenerateId()}" refProjectId="{$projectId}" refProjectStageId="{$stageId}" SortOrder="{@SortOrder}" DateFirstEntered="{AS:iif($currentStageId = $stageId, date:date-time(), '')}" MustFinishBeforeDays="{@MustFinishBeforeDays}" refBusinessPartnerId="{$keyAccountId}" /> </xsl:when>
<!-- stage exists in the history and it is being ENTERED, we update time --> <xsl:when test="string($historyEntry/@Id) and $currentStageId = $stageId"> <xsl:for-each select="$historyEntry"> <xsl:copy> <xsl:copy-of select="@*"/>
<xsl:choose> <xsl:when test="string(@DateFirstEntered)"> <xsl:attribute name="DateLastEntered"><xsl:value-of select="date:date-time()"/></xsl:attribute> </xsl:when> <xsl:otherwise> <xsl:attribute name="DateFirstEntered"><xsl:value-of select="date:date-time()"/></xsl:attribute> <xsl:attribute name="refBusinessPartnerId"><xsl:value-of select="$keyAccountId"/></xsl:attribute> </xsl:otherwise> </xsl:choose>
<xsl:copy-of select="*"/> </xsl:copy> </xsl:for-each> </xsl:when>
<!-- stage exists in the history and it is being EXITED, we update time --> <xsl:when test="string($prevHistoryEntry/@Id) and $previousStageId = $stageId"> <xsl:for-each select="$prevHistoryEntry"> <xsl:copy> <xsl:copy-of select="@*"/>
<xsl:choose> <xsl:when test="string(@DateFirstFinished)"> <xsl:attribute name="DateLastFinished"><xsl:value-of select="date:date-time()"/></xsl:attribute> </xsl:when> <xsl:otherwise> <xsl:attribute name="DateFirstFinished"><xsl:value-of select="date:date-time()"/></xsl:attribute> </xsl:otherwise> </xsl:choose>
<xsl:copy-of select="*"/> </xsl:copy> </xsl:for-each> </xsl:when> </xsl:choose> </xsl:template> </xsl:stylesheet>

<xsl:template match="ProjectCategoryStageTaskTemplate"> <xsl:variable name="resourceIdByRole"> <xsl:call-template name="getResourceByRole"> <xsl:with-param name="roleId" select="@refBusinessPartnerRoleTypeId"/> <xsl:with-param name="projectId" select="$projectId"/> <xsl:with-param name="projectManagerId" select="$projectManagerId"/> <xsl:with-param name="keyAccountId" select="$keyAccountId"/> </xsl:call-template> </xsl:variable>

SchemaItem.Name: OnProjectCreated
SchemaItem.M01:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <xsl:stylesheet xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" version="1.0" xmlns:AS="http://schema.advantages.cz/AsapFunctions" xmlns:date="http://exslt.org/dates-and-times" exclude-result-prefixes="AS date">
<xsl:template match="Project"> <ROOT> <xsl:copy> <xsl:copy-of select = "@*"/> <xsl:variable name="CounterCode"><xsl:value-of select="AS:LookupValue('7dbcc451-0df3-4225-8aa0-54de1f291bec', @refProjectTypeId)"/></xsl:variable> <xsl:variable name="Suffix"><xsl:value-of select="AS:LookupValue('75e42edd-ef22-407e-b5a3-ca11352b58da', @refBusinessUnitId)"/></xsl:variable> <xsl:attribute name="ReferenceCode"><xsl:value-of select="concat(AS:GenerateSerial($CounterCode, @DateCreated), '-', $Suffix)"/></xsl:attribute> <xsl:copy-of select = "*"/> </xsl:copy> </ROOT> </xsl:template> </xsl:stylesheet>

SchemaItem.Name: Project_GeneratePapers_from_Stage
SchemaItem.M01:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <xsl:stylesheet xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" version="1.0" xmlns:AS="http://schema.advantages.cz/AsapFunctions" xmlns:date="http://exslt.org/dates-and-times" exclude-result-prefixes="AS date">
<xsl:param name="projectId"/>
<xsl:template match="ROOT"> <ROOT> <xsl:apply-templates select="ProjectCategoryStage/ProjectCategoryPaperTemplate"/> </ROOT> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="ProjectCategoryPaperTemplate"> <ProjectPaper Id="{AS:GenerateId()}" refProjectId="{$projectId}" refBusinessPartnerId="{@refBusinessPartnerId}" TemplateCode="{@TemplateCode}" Name="{@Name}" refResourceAccessLevelId="{@refResourceAccessLevelId}" >
<xsl:if test="string(@DateDueDays)"> <xsl:attribute name="DateDue"><xsl:value-of select="AS:AddDays(substring-before(date:date-time(), 'T'), @DateDueDays)"/></xsl:attribute> </xsl:if>
<Remark><xsl:value-of select="Remark"/></Remark>
<xsl:apply-templates select="Attachment"/> </ProjectPaper> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="Attachment"> <xsl:copy> <xsl:copy-of select="@*"/> <xsl:attribute name="Id"><xsl:value-of select="AS:GenerateId()"/></xsl:attribute> <!-- entity: ProjectPaper --> <xsl:attribute name="refParentRecordEntityId">d449c102-e341-4a04-aedb-ef9d11a11b73</xsl:attribute> <xsl:copy-of select="*"/> </xsl:copy> </xsl:template> </xsl:stylesheet>

SchemaItem.Name: _projectTask_FromTemplate
SchemaItem.M01:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <xsl:stylesheet xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" version="1.0" xmlns:AS="http://schema.advantages.cz/AsapFunctions" xmlns:date="http://exslt.org/dates-and-times" exclude-result-prefixes="AS date">
<xsl:template name="ProjectTaskFromTemplate"> <xsl:param name="resourceId"/> <xsl:param name="responsibleRsourceId"/>
<xsl:attribute name="Id"><xsl:value-of select="AS:GenerateId()"/></xsl:attribute> <xsl:attribute name="IsDelivery"><xsl:value-of select="@IsDelivery"/></xsl:attribute> <xsl:attribute name="Name"><xsl:value-of select="@Name"/></xsl:attribute> <xsl:attribute name="TimeEstimationHours"><xsl:value-of select="@TimeEstimationHours"/></xsl:attribute> <xsl:attribute name="refResourceId"><xsl:value-of select="AS:isnull($resourceId, AS:isnull(@refResourceId, AS:ResourceIdByActiveProfile()))"/></xsl:attribute> <xsl:attribute name="refResponsibleResourceId"><xsl:value-of select="AS:isnull($responsibleRsourceId, AS:isnull(@refResponsibleResourceId, AS:ResourceIdByActiveProfile()))"/></xsl:attribute> <xsl:attribute name="refProjectTaskCategoryId"><xsl:value-of select="@refProjectTaskCategoryId"/></xsl:attribute> <xsl:attribute name="refBlockProjectStageId"><xsl:value-of select="@refBlockProjectStageId"/></xsl:attribute> <xsl:attribute name="refDateByProjectStageId"><xsl:value-of select="@refDateByProjectStageId"/></xsl:attribute> <xsl:attribute name="MustFinishBeforeDaysFromStage"><xsl:value-of select="@MustFinishBeforeDaysFromStage"/></xsl:attribute> <xsl:attribute name="refResourceAccessLevelId"><xsl:value-of select="@refResourceAccessLevelId"/></xsl:attribute>
<xsl:if test="string(@MustFinishBeforeDays)"> <xsl:attribute name="MustFinishBefore"><xsl:value-of select="AS:AddDays(substring-before(date:date-time(), 'T'), @MustFinishBeforeDays)"/></xsl:attribute> </xsl:if> <xsl:if test="string(@DateFromDays)"> <xsl:attribute name="DateFrom"><xsl:value-of select="AS:AddDays(substring-before(date:date-time(), 'T'), @DateFromDays)"/></xsl:attribute> </xsl:if> <xsl:if test="string(@DateToDays)"> <xsl:attribute name="DateTo"><xsl:value-of select="AS:AddDays(substring-before(date:date-time(), 'T'), @DateToDays)"/></xsl:attribute> </xsl:if> <xsl:if test="string(Description)"> <Description><xsl:value-of select="Description"/></Description> </xsl:if> </xsl:template> </xsl:stylesheet>
